{"tid":2353806,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"馬道立回應三權分立：基本法確實列明有獨立司法權 現在成為政治爭議非他本意","createTime":"2021-01-05T04:34:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-05T05:52:51.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b99c8389234db6771e0133b02a9212688bc79aeb","tid":2353806,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T04:34:49.000Z","msg":"馬道立：國安法有挑戰但同樣按法律裁決案件<br />\n<br />\n馬道立回應提問時指，處理港區國安法與其他法律問題一樣有挑戰，但法院亦是一樣的態度，按法律理據裁決案件勝負及定罪，強調法院只處理法律而非政治問題。<br />\n<br />\n馬道立又回應2014年法律年度開啟典禮致辭時，曾提及「三權分立」原則。他指當時並非想提出政治問題，現時「三權分立」用字亦變成政治爭議，而他希望強調的是，基本法其中三條條文強調，香港有司法獨立，最重要是記得這一點，重申他只講法律而非政治。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2373486\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2373486&d=zT4eWHrghymhx70gWSuuOVyVYJ%2BaYT2AGLfERhQaW2c%3D&h=45a0177e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2373486</a>"},{"pid":"4f164d88ae2028ecf184fc9606a35e822f41e352","tid":2353806,"uid":99397,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T04:38:17.000Z","msg":"呢條友跟本口交部嚟，你直接話依家係三權合作同大陸無分別，無咁嬲。"},{"pid":"3e47a5d2e197e69ab4624711ee7b7f07485d11d1","tid":2353806,"uid":72185,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T05:00:43.000Z","msg":"咁鹿生果日你又跑咁快?"},{"pid":"67b0f08ff5b6586525b714c8839c3a102ea023d3","tid":2353806,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T05:02:54.000Z","msg":"共產走狗！賣港賊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bda5bb990218a218c0fc5631b96085b0461e3aaf","tid":2353806,"uid":204539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e47a5d